1.INHERETANCE
2.


===============================INHERITANCEE================================


mekedi wenne code eka reuse wena eka
apita parent class eke tina attributes and methods use karannath puluwan
ewagema new methods and attributes use karannath puluwan.

WHY WE USE INHERITANCE
	basically for code reuse
	for method overwriding 
	
mekedi EXTEND kiyala key word ekak use karanawa.
	eg-    public class childclass extends parentclass
			keep that on mind 
			
TYPES OF INHERITANCE 
	mekedi 3 types of inheritance tinawa
	1.single           me tika thamai java wala tina inheritance
	2.multilevel
	3.Hierarchical
		multiple  hybrid inheritance java valadi use wenne naha.
		diamond effect eka mathak karanna.(diamaond effect kiyala addinne hybrid inheritance eka thamai)
		
WHY MULTIPLE INHERITANCE IS NOT SUPPORTED IN JAVA
	mekidi wenne api hithamu  A B C class tinawa kiyala 
				A      B
				 \    /
					c      mekedi  run() kiyala function ekak A and B ta tibbama eka C tath enawa.C walin run call kaloth mona 
					run ekada call wenne.so there is an ambuguity.so to reduce the complexity and simplyfy the language.

=============================AGGREGATION====================================================================

	mekide wenne class ekak athule thawath class ekaka object ekak use wena eka.
		eg- class person ekate api Address address kiyala object ekak haduwai kiyala kiyamu.
			address eke attrubutes widihata lane,street gannawa.ita passe ekenn object ekak hadala e object eka person ekata pass 
			karana eka thama karanne. 
		
		